    @deprecated 0.13.0
      @description 
        Use @code[min(value)] instead.
        

    @added 0.10.0
    @description 
      Sets the minimum value the number picker can have

    @arg min [Number]
      @description 
        The minimum value the number picker can have
        

    @return NumberPicker
      @description 
        This NumberPicker
        

  @method setMax
    @removed 0.14.0
      @description 
        Use @code[max(value)] instead.
        

